title: U.S., South Korea agree in principle on new trade deal - White House
text:
U.S., South Korea agree in principle on new trade deal - White House Wednesday, March 28, 2018 - 00:30 
The United States and South Korea have reached agreement in principle on a new trade pact and details will be released soon, the White House said on Tuesday. Rough Cut (no reporter narration). ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
